    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>peri peri sauce</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) to a separate large bowl with the <strong>free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> and mix well until fully coated</p><p>Transfer the <strong>coated</strong> <strong>chicken</strong> to a baking tray (use <strong>tin foil</strong> to avoid mess!) and put the tray in the oven for 18-20 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>peri peri chicken</strong></p>",
